•	employee relations;

*Responsible for End-to-End Recruitment;
 *associated with BFSI and IT sector recruitment; 
*Analysing, understanding & managing clients requirements ; 
*Sourcing & screening candidate's profiles through various means like job portals, headhunting, references, social networking, etc.;
 *Matching the relevancy of candidates profiles with the requirements being shared by the clients ; 
